title: Checkmk Notification Spooler: Connection
agents: linux
catalog: app/cmk
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check checks the status of indiviual TCP connections from a
 Checkmk Notification Spooler to a remote spooler. For each incoming
 and outoing TCP connection one service will be created. The state goes
 critical if the connection is not up.

item:
 The name of the site followed by a dash followed by the name of the
 connected remote site. If more than one incoming connections exist
 from the same remote host then an index will be appended.

discovery:
 One sevice is created for each site and connection.
